This project is using git submodules. They are not included in zipball or tarball. Hence
it is recommended that you fetch the source code with git clone by doing:

1.

git clone --recursive https://github.com/lano1106/glcs.git

2.

git clone https://github.com/lano1106/glcs.git
git submodule init
git submodule update

For building and installing, you can use the 2 provided bash scripts or get packages for ArchLinux

at https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/glcs/

